      "writtenOn": "2021-06-28T01:15:42Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The Vadim\u0027s approach sounds good to me.\nWe can append the realm for reproduction to the response of task API for the UI.\n\n\u003e Then Swarming can look it up based on the original tasks\u0027s realm.\n\nIIUC, api.get_realm_data() is the API that Swarming needs to call. Is my understanding correct?\nhttps://source.chromium.org/chromium/infra/infra/+/main:luci/appengine/components/components/auth/api.py;l\u003d876?q\u003df:luci%20%22def%20has_permission%22\u0026ss\u003dchromium",
      "parentUuid": "578bd107_6f4ef337",
